channel.title: Mod Party and Cat Duping (WARNING: LOTS OF PICS)
channel.description:
[glow=red,2,300]These are not fakes, they are all screenies. I got invited to a Mod Party and 2 J mods decided to show up. There was around 20-40 P mods :O. The second set of pics are glitch screenies of me and a friend cat duping. He used hellcats, I used clockcats. I edited out my name because I posted this on a few sites.[/glow]
[b]Chris changed his level to 1:[/b] [img]http://img207.imageshack.us/img207/9027/untitledyi7.jpg[/img]
[b]Ahh. Look how he's dressed. OMG duck zombie meat-tenderizer boy:[/b] [img]http://img224.imageshack.us/img224/5535/untitled2ax7.jpg[/img]
[b]Emilee decided to teleport to an unreachable island:[/b] [img]http://img207.imageshack.us/img207/9309/untitled3kz4.jpg[/img]
[b]Emilee decided to cut chat on for a bit:[/b] [img]http://img224.imageshack.us/img224/7674/untitled6lk7.jpg[/img]
[b]Emilee hax0rs:[/b] [img]http://img224.imageshack.us/img224/7055/untitled5db8.jpg[/img] [glow=red,2,300] ________________________________________________________________________________________________[/glow] [glow=red,2,300]Few pics of a cat duping glitch. Me and friend did. The reason it says Welcome to RuneScape is because in order to make the cats scatter, you had to log out. ________________________________________________________________________________________________[/glow]
[b]Fally:[/b] [img]http://img80.imageshack.us/img80/1852/catshs1.png[/img]
[b]Ardy:[/b] [img]http://img206.imageshack.us/img206/456/7sw5.jpg[/img]
The cat pictures were from a glitch where when you went downstairs in H.A.M. place and back upstairs there would be two cats following you. I did a couple hundred times and then logged out in random place. The cats would scatter except for my original one. The 'duped' cats showed up like it wasn't my cat when I tried to pick it up, yet it followed me.
